{"tid":2289134,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Naver創始人的兒子「LØREN」以歌手身份正式出道！曾出演BLACKPINK MV男主角","createTime":"2020-11-17T04:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T10:08:44.000Z","uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bccf142f86f41f27c1a5051d99135ec4023fdd9c","tid":2289134,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T04:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_bf6b515bc0443f18bbe2ea17b3bc7b56/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131684-885048.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_bf6b515bc0443f18bbe2ea17b3bc7b56%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131684-885048.jpg&h=5b8d2577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNaver的創始人兼全球投資負責人李海鎮（音，이해진）的兒子李升洲（音，이승주）以「L&Oslash;REN」作為藝名，以歌手身份正式出道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n13日，通過YG旗下廠牌The Black Label公開出道曲《EMPTY TRASH》音源、MV，他不僅負責作詞、作曲、編曲，還演奏所有樂器。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_7d94687e9330d2acd7a56b73a70187e1/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131684-885040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_7d94687e9330d2acd7a56b73a70187e1%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131684-885040.jpg&h=4d34b680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他和BLACKPINK也有著與衆不同的緣分，在BLACKPINK的首張正規專輯《THE ALBUM》中，他參與了《Pretty Savage》、《Lovesick Girls》和《You Never Know》的作詞，還出演《Lovesick Girls》MV的男主角。<br />\n<br />\n雖然The Black Label通過官方SNS宣傳L&Oslash;REN的出道曲，但他並不是旗下的歌手。The Black Label方面表示：「L&Oslash;REN並不是The Black Label旗下的歌手，就像製作宣美的《Gashina》一樣，這只是我們進行的項目之一。」有興趣的朋友，可以去聽聽他的歌哦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9f28Pi14g0w&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9f28Pi14g0w%26feature%3Demb_title&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM43ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=3f6c5060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9f28Pi14g0w&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n（圖：IG@lorenisalone、IG@oses_are_rosi、BLACKPINK《Lovesick Girls》MV）"},{"pid":"909e970648e8a88a59ef419893ec3bccef726fdd","tid":2289134,"uid":84668,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"幪面超人555呀？"},{"pid":"8c060c90ebf773bfa7597a65f26745d9c66b8e32","tid":2289134,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":29,"score":-24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T04:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b10bde0c9355f0fc966ac4cdf813e528/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131684-885045.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b10bde0c9355f0fc966ac4cdf813e528%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131684-885045.jpg&h=36526fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0163e86aef85746f1663dce926a71798/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131684-885046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0163e86aef85746f1663dce926a71798%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131684-885046.jpg&h=1a8db3c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c19e8c497beb89c24e14ae5364e2fcccfa440fc5","tid":2289134,"uid":263183,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c060c90ebf773bfa7597a65f26745d9c66b8e32","tid":2289134,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":29,"score":-24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T04:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b10bde0c9355f0fc966ac4cdf813e528/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131684-885045.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b10bde0c9355f0fc966ac4cdf813e528%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131684-885045.jpg&h=36526fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0163e86aef85746f1663dce926a71798/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131684-885046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0163e86aef85746f1663dce926a717